{"tid":217933,"cid":13,"subCid":0,"title":"美版champion tee 92蚊2件 有無人一齊夾運費～～‼️‼️找數","createTime":"2017-04-26T07:00:54.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-07T00:01:03.000Z","uid":30990,"like":1,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"8d4174d8506d6c965056c735057fd231c782347d","tid":217933,"uid":30990,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-26T07:00:54.000Z","msg":"各位巴絲你地好呀，咁我為免有人話我買淘寶貨或其他a貨溝水摸魚 咁我開個post証明我有真實收據，當然有d人可能會話：我買完拎張單再溝淘寶貨唔得咩。咁呢樣野講<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">信任</span></strong></span>   而家連登仔起人底咁易 如果我溝假野 實比人好快起底 <br />\n<br />\n好多巴絲都有搵我一齊夾買champion tee 多謝你地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n因為都多人買同有d碼無所以好快截左數，如果其他巴絲仲想買可以上返champion 官網訂<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.champion.com/shop/champion/clearance--1/up-to-off/clearance-priced#facet:&amp;productBeginlindex:0&amp;orderBy:&amp;pageView:grid&amp;minPrice:&amp;maxPrice:&amp;pageSize:20&amp;\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.champion.com%2Fshop%2Fchampion%2Fclearance--1%2Fup-to-off%2Fclearance-priced%23facet%3A%26productBeginlindex%3A0%26orderBy%3A%26pageView%3Agrid%26minPrice%3A%26maxPrice%3A%26pageSize%3A20%26&d=aJB%2Bq6ruafnyRbkwc%2FW5ZgdLCpCjoNGxXEizPMjNmRM%3D&h=b07e37fa\" target=\"_blank\">www.champion.com/shop/champion/clearance--1/up-to-off/clearance-priced#facet:&amp;productBeginlindex:0&amp;orderBy:&amp;pageView:grid&amp;minPrice:&amp;maxPrice:&amp;pageSize:20&amp;</a><br />\n或者如果巴絲打想既話我都可以幫你地訂<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">Tg:waion</span> 有問題可以隨時搵我 我估講到呢到可能又有人話我想賺錢<br />\n<br />\n❗❗我同每個巴絲講都係65蚊一件計埋運費，如果你話點解咁貴 <span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">因為</span>第二張單既運費比較貴 所以我將2張單夾埋balance返。<br />\n<br />\n❗❗有d巴打可能話我食水，咁車費 交收都要少少錢  我真心想大家可以減輕運費之餘仲買到平野，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">如果</span>你覺得我食水深 你唔想買既 我可以退返錢比你 <br />\n<br />\n今次係我第一次開團，我初初見到ig shop 好似好平 之後上官網睇原來仲平 但運費貴到痴線 先忍唔住開post睇下有無其他其絲一齊夾運 多謝咁多位巴絲打<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/04/26/143259_8db96f1f0cc594337e90eae57897b167.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F04%2F26%2F143259_8db96f1f0cc594337e90eae57897b167.jpg&h=13d51a84&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/04/26/143246_7c10796385166ec2d1cca685d4cac57f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F04%2F26%2F143246_7c10796385166ec2d1cca685d4cac57f.jpg&h=0a997c27&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/04/26/143241_e844064a3f99e62e4c9823cdbe5bfccf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F04%2F26%2F143241_e844064a3f99e62e4c9823cdbe5bfccf.jpg&h=6dd0219d&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/04/26/143303_f90925425ca8ac665d98633e5dbcdc27.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F04%2F26%2F143303_f90925425ca8ac665d98633e5dbcdc27.jpg&h=11882f98&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/04/26/143308_4416d17a8fdaab8bef66bc40b916b434.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F04%2F26%2F143308_4416d17a8fdaab8bef66bc40b916b434.jpg&h=5d9e0978&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"187bf0c6360ce916c316924b91a13627886e85d7","tid":217933,"uid":108120,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-26T07:50:46.000Z","msg":"開完又開"},{"pid":"63167b8d941ce4782a1faea695f4c5ed3d9290d1","tid":217933,"uid":88029,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-26T08:23:43.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"8d57e8bc729e3e661233631b4e0bc90a01eb0847","tid":217933,"uid":64078,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTi